[03/07/2019 09:59:17] <font color="#00ffff">Sí.</font>
[03/07/2019 09:59:17] <font color="#ffff00">¿Es así?</font>
[03/07/2019 09:59:19] <font color="#00ff00">Sí, claro.</font>
